snippet.title: Best VGM 2432 - Mario Kart Wii - DK Summit
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 182 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0Y1Y3buSm2I
Best VGM 465 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HXxA7QJTycA

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo Wii
Mario Kart Wii (2008)
DK Summit
Asuka Ohta & Ryo Nagamatsu
